            <title>[CASSANDRA-13512] SASI full-text search queries using standard analyzer do not work in multi-node environments</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-13512</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SASI full-text search queries using standard analyzer do not work in multi-node environments. Standard Analyzer will rewind the buffer and search term will be empty for any node other than coordinator, so will return no results.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
