	&lt;li&gt;I seems there is a typo &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/ifesdjeen/cassandra-dtest/blob/55334ebb724eb5224572c7f58c4f6157bf1780cd/cql_tests.py#L1442&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;, &quot;dests&quot; by &quot;dtests&quot;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;This is only a suggestion, I think it would be nice to break &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/ifesdjeen/cassandra-dtest/blob/55334ebb724eb5224572c7f58c4f6157bf1780cd/cql_tests.py#L1466&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;this line&lt;/a&gt; to satisfy the 120 char width.&lt;/li&gt;
